data.description:
Welcome to your new home! With a full price offer The 2019 Ex-Go golf cart stays, owner has the title, 2 new extra tires and a jack. It has 6 new batteries and has been serviced annually. Just have to get a license and it will be street legal. Back patio furniture:  rectangle glass table with 4 chairs, blue coach, 2 chairs, 2 foot stools, 2 round rugs ( 1 blue, 1 red) and coffee table.
Did we mention the 2.375%  assumable VA loan?  As you pull up, you will notice the sitting area in front and the easy care desert landscaping.  Once inside, you have a bedroom and bath in front with a view to the back straight ahead.  As you come down the hall with wood look tile you will have your side patio on the left and then the house opens up to the kitchen with lighted glass doors on either side of the stove, a center island and quartz counters. To the right beside the patio is your den overlooking your backyard. You master suite is in the back right and opens to the bath with dual sinks and a large walk-in closet.  The pantry and large laundry room are next to the kitchen and take you to the garage where storage abounds.  The Whirlpool refrigerator in the pantry stays with the house. This is one of the rare homes with a Taexx pest control system.  Best of all, this house has an assumable 2.375% loan if you qualify.

 All of this in the 55+ guard gated lake community of Province where you can fish in the lakes, take a walk on one of the 5 miles of walking paths throughout the community, practice your putting, play a game of pickleball or tennis is nothing
short of "retiring like you mean it!" To wrap it all up, inside the 32,000 square foot clubhouse, you have a fitness center, lap pool,
library, billiards room, ceramic, sewing, and computer center besides the quaint, gorgeous outdoor pool for perfect solitude or fun gatherings with friends and family. What more could you want?
